<item>
            <title>[LU-10843] snapshot_create fails after MGS restart</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10843</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the MGS is unmounted and remount (or failed over) &lt;tt&gt;lctl snapshot_create&lt;/tt&gt; fails with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# lctl snapshot_create -F scratch -n test
Fail to freeze barrier for scratch: No such device
Can&apos;t create the snapshot test
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;snapshot_destroy still works without issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;WORKAROUND:&lt;/b&gt; unmount/mount the MDT and &lt;tt&gt;snapshot_create&lt;/tt&gt; will commence working again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;NOTE:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;tt&gt;mount -o remount&lt;/tt&gt; is insufficient&lt;/p&gt;</description>
